parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the parking brake can cause the rear brakes to wear prematurely, generate excessive heat, and potentially lead to accidents or loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the power brake booster can make it difficult to stop the vehicle, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
Failure of the rear brake caliper can cause uneven brake pad wear, premature wear of brake components, and potentially lead to accidents or loss of control.
Delayed recall repairs can leave vehicles with potentially faulty brake systems, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
